metadata.name: My True Treasure
metadata.description:
Momo-chan just discovered a new treasure from an other world, an infinite source of love: the shikigami IROIRO-Coin !

This art was created in April, 2023 for the IROIRO Illustration Contest.
Fan art of IROIRO PFP #779.

Created by Rodger Liukane
Approx. time: 30hr
Procreate, Illustrator, AfterEffects and Cinema4D
Seamless loop in MP4
2480x3508px [A4 paper size]
